data.description: Welcome to 4272 Encinitas Way, Union City! This charming 2-level townhouse unit is now available for sale. With 2 bedrooms and 1.5 bathrooms, this home offers a comfortable and convenient living space. The main level features a bright and airy living area, where you can relax and unwind. Step into your U-shape kitchen, perfect for preparing meals and entertaining guests. Upstairs, you'll discover two cozy bedrooms, providing space for rest and relaxation. The full bathroom on this level offers a tranquil retreat. This townhouse unit also boasts a 2-car garage, ensuring that you have plenty of space for parking and storage. Additionally, the in-unit washer and dryer make laundry day a breeze. Step outside and enjoy the open backyard, perfect for outdoor activities and gatherings. The enclosed front yard adds an extra layer of security. Located in the desirable Union City Townhouse neighborhood, this home offers easy access to nearby amenities, including shopping centers, restaurants, parks, and schools. With its convenient location and comfortable living spaces, this townhouse unit is the perfect place to call home.
